sentences: Paula Mitrache (born June 14, 1977), known by the stage name Haiducii (Romanian pronunciation: [hajˈdutʃij]), is a Romanian-Italian singer, model and actress.
She released her debut single "Dragostea din tei" in 2004, acting as a cover of O-Zone's homonymous 2003 single.
Paula Mitrache in Haiducii, the singer's debut studio album, followed in 2008.
